race.comment: NOAKI RADAR (1) goes very well here including three wins. Recorded a 7 length win (19.46) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. With a clean break looks hard to beat. DING DING HARROW (8) got around 352m in a swift 19.73 when winning a Grade 5 at this track last start. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. GRANDIOSE GIRL (6) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from nine starts. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (19.61) in a Grade 5 over 352m at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. TUSKEN WARRIOR (7) has won at this course and distance so worth including.
